description:
This is a 36 minute workout called '30 Min Weight Training for Weight Loss and Strength - Home Full Body Dumbbell Workout for Women Men' from the channel HASfit.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.
